description: At Cooper's Crepes we believe it's our job to tickle your taste buds and bring you great food that is new, fun and sweet.  But most importantly, our crepes are made to order hot off our crepe grill and we don't tolerate any skimping on our fillings. (Honestly… It just wouldn’t be right.)Cooper's Crepes is a mobile unit with a fresh look and you can find us roaming around Cincinnati. Catch us on a curbside near you!
name: Cooper's Crepes
